<template>
  <canvas></canvas>
</template>
<script>
import * as THREE from 'three'
import * as dat from 'dat.gui'
import Stats from "three/addons/libs/stats.module";

const canvas=document.createElement('canvas')
var stats0 = initStats();

canvas.width=800;
canvas.height=800;

document.body.appendChild(canvas)
const scene=new THREE.Scene();
scene.background=new THREE.Color("white")
const loader = new THREE.TextureLoader();
const renderer = new THREE.WebGLRenderer({canvas:canvas});
const group=new THREE.Object3D();
group.position.set(1,0,0)

const pg= new THREE.PlaneBufferGeometry(1000,200, 1, 1);
const pm = new THREE.MeshBasicMaterial({color: 0xcccccc});
const p = new THREE.Mesh(pg,pm);
p.rotation.x= 15
p.rotation.y=0
p.rotation.z=0
p.rotation.x=-0.5*Math.PI;
scene.add(p)

const yuan = new THREE.SphereGeometry(40, 40, 40);
const texture_2=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/picture/wenli3.jpg');
const material_2 = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: texture_2});
const yuan_object= new THREE.Mesh(yuan, material_2);
yuan_object.position.set(0,40,0)
group.add(yuan_object)


const yuan_2= new THREE.SphereGeometry(4, 4, 4);
const texture_4=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/picture/wenli1.jpg');
const material_4 = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: texture_4});
const yuan_object_2= new THREE.Mesh(yuan_2, material_4);
yuan_object_2.position.set(20,70,20)
group.add(yuan_object_2)
const yuan_3= new THREE.SphereGeometry(4, 4, 4);
const yuan_object_3= new THREE.Mesh(yuan_3, material_4);
yuan_object_3.position.set(20,70,-20)
group.add(yuan_object_3)


const yuan_zhui = new THREE.ConeGeometry(10,50,30);
const texture_3=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/picture/wenli3.jpg');
const material_3 = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: texture_3});
const yuan_zhui_object= new THREE.Mesh(yuan_zhui, material_3);
const yuan_zhui_object_2= new THREE.Mesh(yuan_zhui, material_3);
yuan_zhui_object.position.set(0,80,40)
yuan_zhui_object.rotation.set(45,0,0)
yuan_zhui_object_2.position.set(0,80,-40)
yuan_zhui_object_2.rotation.set(-45,0,0)

const cube1 = new THREE.BoxGeometry(20, 20, 20);
const uptexture=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/api/picture/up.jpg');
const downtexture=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/api/picture/down.jpg');
const lefttexture=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/api/picture/left.jpg');
const righttexture=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/api/picture/right.jpg');
const fronttexture=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/api/picture/front.jpg');
const backtexture=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/api/picture/back.jpg');
const upmaterial = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: uptexture});
const downmaterial = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: downtexture});
const leftmaterial = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: lefttexture});
const rightmaterial = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: righttexture});
const frontmaterial = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: fronttexture});
const backmaterial = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: backtexture});
const material1=[upmaterial,downmaterial,leftmaterial,rightmaterial,frontmaterial,backmaterial]
const cube_object1 = new THREE.Mesh(cube1, material1);
cube_object1.position.set(0,0,0)
group.add(cube_object1);

const cube = new THREE.BoxGeometry(2, 6, 20);
const texture=loader.load('http://114.55.38.94:8001/picture/wenli2.jpg');
const material = new THREE.MeshLambertMaterial({map: texture});
const cube_object = new THREE.Mesh(cube, material);
cube_object.position.set(40,50,0)
cube_object.rotation.set(0,0,0)
group.add(cube_object);

group.add(yuan_zhui_object);
group.add(yuan_zhui_object_2);
scene.add(group)

var ambientLight = new THREE.AmbientLight(0x0c0c0c,1);
scene.add(ambientLight);

var spotLight = new THREE.SpotLight(0xffffff);
spotLight.position.set(50, 100, 0);
spotLight.castShadow = true;
scene.add(spotLight)

var controls = new function () {
  this.rotationSpeed=0
};

const gui=new dat.GUI();
gui.add(controls, 'rotationSpeed', 0, 0.5);

const camera = new THREE.PerspectiveCamera();
//camera.position.set(200, 200, 200);
camera.position.set(200, 200, 200);
camera.lookAt(0, 0, 0);
const axis=new THREE.Vector3(0,1,0)
Render();




function Render() {
  stats0.update();
  scene.traverse(function () {
    //group.rotation.x += controls.rotationSpeed;
    //group.rotation.y += controls.rotationSpeed;
    //group.rotation.z += controls.rotationSpeed;
    group.rotateOnAxis(axis,Math.PI/8*controls.rotationSpeed)
  });
  requestAnimationFrame(Render);
  renderer.render(scene, camera);
}

function initStats() {

  var stats= new Stats();

  stats.setMode(0); // 0: fps, 1: ms

  // Align top-left
  stats.domElement.style.position = 'absolute';
  stats.domElement.style.left = '0px';
  stats.domElement.style.top = '0px';

  canvas.appendChild(stats.domElement);

  return stats;
}



</script>
<style scoped>

</style>
